<div class="title">Caffeine and Sports</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Rear+Admiral&Exact=1">Rear Admiral</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Rear Admiral. "Caffeine and Sports: An Experience with Caffeine (exp36643)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 8, 2007. erowid.org/exp/36643</div>

<br/>



